data.title: Adolph Menzel 1815-1905. Master Drawings From East Berlin
data.meta_description: Alexandria, VA: Art Services International, 1990. Wraps. Very Good. Item #019015 Glossy illustrated wraps. 235 pp. Color and black and white illustrations throughout. A catalog to a 1990 exhibition of drawings, watercolor and gouache paintings by Adolph Menzel, a 19th century German painter who gained popularity due to his historical paintings. VERY GOOD condition. Light scuffing and toning.

Alexandria, VA: Art Services International, 1990. Wraps. Very Good. Item #019015

Glossy illustrated wraps. 235 pp. Color and black and white illustrations throughout. A catalog to a 1990 exhibition of drawings, watercolor and gouache paintings by Adolph Menzel, a 19th century German painter who gained popularity due to his historical paintings. VERY GOOD condition. Light scuffing and toning.
